{
  "video_id": "AhUhpfKeLus",
  "title": "This is what democracy looks like | Anthony D. Romero",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12756.0,
      "end_time": 15180.0,
      "text": "Silicon Valley is obsessed with disruption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16379.000000000002,
      "end_time": 20600.0,
      "text": "but these days, the biggest disruptor didn&#39;t come out of Silicon Valley."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20899.0,
      "end_time": 23300.0,
      "text": "It came out of steel towns in Ohio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24100.0,
      "end_time": 26380.0,
      "text": "rural communities in Pennsylvania,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27420.0,
      "end_time": 29300.0,
      "text": "the Panhandle in Florida."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30820.0,
      "end_time": 33756.0,
      "text": "And this last US presidential election"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33780.0,
      "end_time": 35400.0,
      "text": "was the mother of all disruptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36980.0,
      "end_time": 39779.0,
      "text": "Once again, politics is personal."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40940.0,
      "end_time": 44355.0,
      "text": "Millions of Americans became activists overnight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44380.0,
      "end_time": 47196.0,
      "text": "pouring into the streets in record numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47220.0,
      "end_time": 48635.0,
      "text": "in record time."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48660.0,
      "end_time": 50476.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50500.0,
      "end_time": 52836.0,
      "text": "The election has done to family holiday dinners"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52860.0,
      "end_time": 55620.0,
      "text": "what Uber has done to New York City&#39;s taxi system."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57600.0,
      "end_time": 59940.0,
      "text": "Couples have broken up and marriages disrupted."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61980.0,
      "end_time": 64750.0,
      "text": "And the election is doing to my private life"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64989.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66140.0,
      "text": "what Amazon is doing to shopping malls."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66660.0,
      "end_time": 71200.0,
      "text": "These days, the ACLU is on the front lines 24/7,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71940.0,
      "end_time": 75860.0,
      "text": "and even if I manage to sneak away for a couple of miles on the treadmill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77590.0,
      "end_time": 80876.0,
      "text": "any cardio benefit I get is instantly obliterated"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80900.0,
      "end_time": 84340.0,
      "text": "when I read another presidential tweet on the headline scroll."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86100.0,
      "end_time": 88756.0,
      "text": "Even my secret pleasure"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88780.0,
      "end_time": 91276.0,
      "text": "of studying the Italian painters"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 91300.0,
      "end_time": 93500.0,
      "text": "have been infected by politics."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 94540.0,
      "end_time": 97380.0,
      "text": "Now, I study, even stalk, the old masters."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98100.0,
      "end_time": 99675.0,
      "text": "This is my desk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99700.0,
      "end_time": 101516.0,
      "text": "with a postcard exhibition"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 101540.0,
      "end_time": 103396.0,
      "text": "of some famous and obscure paintings"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103420.0,
      "end_time": 105420.0,
      "text": "mostly from the Italian Renaissance."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106100.0,
      "end_time": 108556.0,
      "text": "Now, art used to provide me with a necessary break"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108580.0,
      "end_time": 110876.0,
      "text": "from the hurly-burly of politics"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110900.0,
      "end_time": 113276.0,
      "text": "in my daily work at the ACLU,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113300.0,
      "end_time": 114500.0,
      "text": "but not anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115380.0,
      "end_time": 117436.0,
      "text": "I was at the Women&#39;s March in San Francisco"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117460.0,
      "end_time": 118996.0,
      "text": "the day after inauguration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119200.0,
      "end_time": 122760.0,
      "text": "and the crowd was chanting, \"This is what democracy looks like.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122100.0,
      "end_time": 124259.0,
      "text": "\"This is what democracy looks like.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125380.0,
      "end_time": 129356.0,
      "text": "And there I was holding my sign and my umbrella in the rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129380.0,
      "end_time": 133196.0,
      "text": "and I flashed on an old painting"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133220.0,
      "end_time": 135340.0,
      "text": "that first captivated me many years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136340.0,
      "end_time": 139676.0,
      "text": "I struggled to remember the different pieces"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139700.0,
      "end_time": 142360.0,
      "text": "of an actual painting"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142600.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "of good and bad government."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144980.0,
      "end_time": 147459.0,
      "text": "It was almost like the old master was taunting me."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148140.0,
      "end_time": 150179.0,
      "text": "You want to know what democracy looks like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150660.0,
      "end_time": 152540.0,
      "text": "Go back and look at my frescoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153780.0,
      "end_time": 154980.0,
      "text": "And so I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155980.0,
      "end_time": 161756.0,
      "text": "In 1339, Ambrogio Lorenzetti finished a monumental commission"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 161780.0,
      "end_time": 165200.0,
      "text": "in the governing council chamber of Siena&#39;s Palazzo Pubblico."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 165620.0,
      "end_time": 169820.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a painting that speaks to us, even screams to us, today."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172300.0,
      "end_time": 176760.0,
      "text": "\"Art is a lie that makes us realize truth,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 176100.0,
      "end_time": 177780.0,
      "text": "Pablo Picasso once said."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 178500.0,
      "end_time": 180756.0,
      "text": "And as we search for the truth about government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 180780.0,
      "end_time": 182676.0,
      "text": "we should keep Ambrogio&#39;s work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 182700.0,
      "end_time": 186980.0,
      "text": "not a lie but an allegory, in our collective mind&#39;s eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 188380.0,
      "end_time": 189796.0,
      "text": "During Lorenzetti&#39;s time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189820.0,
      "end_time": 193116.0,
      "text": "the political legitimacy of Italian city-states"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 193140.0,
      "end_time": 195590.0,
      "text": "was often on very shaky ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195620.0,
      "end_time": 197476.0,
      "text": "Siena was a republic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 197500.0,
      "end_time": 199156.0,
      "text": "but there had been enormous unrest"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199180.0,
      "end_time": 201420.0,
      "text": "in the two decades leading up to the commission."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 202600.0,
      "end_time": 205356.0,
      "text": "Siena&#39;s political leaders, who would literally govern"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 205380.0,
      "end_time": 208555.0,
      "text": "under the eyes of these allegorical figures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 208580.0,
      "end_time": 210820.0,
      "text": "were Lorenzetti&#39;s intended audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211540.0,
      "end_time": 213756.0,
      "text": "He was cataloging the obligations"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 213780.0,
      "end_time": 216620.0,
      "text": "of the governing to the governed."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 218220.0,
      "end_time": 221236.0,
      "text": "Now, you can spend years studying these frescoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 222660.0,
      "text": "Some scholars have."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223180.0,
      "end_time": 225316.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m hardly an art historian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 225340.0,
      "end_time": 227916.0,
      "text": "but I am passionate about art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227940.0,
      "end_time": 230516.0,
      "text": "and a work this massive can overwhelm me."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 230540.0,
      "end_time": 232980.0,
      "text": "So first, I focus on the big stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 235620.0,
      "end_time": 238540.0,
      "text": "This is the allegory of good government."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 239580.0,
      "end_time": 241796.0,
      "text": "The majestic figure here in the middle"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 241820.0,
      "end_time": 244236.0,
      "text": "is dressed in Siena&#39;s colors"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247190.0,
      "text": "and he personifies the republic itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248200.0,
      "end_time": 251760.0,
      "text": "Lorenzetti labels him \"Commune,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 251100.0,
      "end_time": 253756.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s basically telling the Sienese"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 253780.0,
      "end_time": 257860.0,
      "text": "that they, and not a king or a tyrant, must rule themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 258940.0,
      "end_time": 262700.0,
      "text": "Now, surrounding Commune are his advisors."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 265580.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "Justice is enthroned."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267700.0,
      "end_time": 270836.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s looking up at the figure of wisdom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 270860.0,
      "end_time": 274180.0,
      "text": "who actually supports her scales of justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276820.0,
      "end_time": 279356.0,
      "text": "Concord, or Harmony,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279380.0,
      "end_time": 282516.0,
      "text": "holds a string that comes off the scales of justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282540.0,
      "end_time": 284556.0,
      "text": "that binds her to the citizens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 284580.0,
      "end_time": 287380.0,
      "text": "making them all compatriots in the republic."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 290200.0,
      "end_time": 291676.0,
      "text": "And finally we see Peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 291700.0,
      "end_time": 293156.0,
      "text": "She looks chilled out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 293180.0,
      "end_time": 295556.0,
      "text": "like she&#39;s listening to Bob Marley."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 295580.0,
      "end_time": 297556.0,
      "text": "When good government rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 297580.0,
      "end_time": 299460.0,
      "text": "Peace doesn&#39;t break a sweat."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 300600.0,
      "end_time": 302476.0,
      "text": "Now, these are big images and big ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 302500.0,
      "end_time": 304700.0,
      "text": "but I really love the small stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 305300.0,
      "end_time": 306716.0,
      "text": "Along another wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 306740.0,
      "end_time": 310760.0,
      "text": "Lorenzetti illustrates the effects of good government"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 310100.0,
      "end_time": 312476.0,
      "text": "on the real and everyday lives of ordinary people"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312500.0,
      "end_time": 315380.0,
      "text": "with a series of delicious little details."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 320940.0,
      "text": "In the countryside, the hills are landscaped and farmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 323100.0,
      "end_time": 326796.0,
      "text": "Crops are being sown, hoed, reaped, milled, plowed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 326820.0,
      "end_time": 328219.0,
      "text": "all in one picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 330820.0,
      "end_time": 333540.0,
      "text": "Crops and livestock are being brought to market."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 335300.0,
      "end_time": 337620.0,
      "text": "In the city, builders raise a tower."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 340220.0,
      "end_time": 344360.0,
      "text": "People attend a law lecture, a TED Talk of the 14th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 344600.0,
      "end_time": 345620.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347100.0,
      "end_time": 348740.0,
      "text": "Schoolchildren play."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 350860.0,
      "end_time": 352580.0,
      "text": "Tradesmen thrive."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 354820.0,
      "end_time": 357780.0,
      "text": "Dancers larger than life dance with joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 360220.0,
      "end_time": 363740.0,
      "text": "And watching over the republic is the winged figure Security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 364380.0,
      "end_time": 365836.0,
      "text": "whose banner reads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 365860.0,
      "end_time": 369540.0,
      "text": "\"Everyone shall go forth freely without fear.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 371600.0,
      "end_time": 373756.0,
      "text": "Now, what&#39;s amazing about these images from 800 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 373780.0,
      "end_time": 375700.0,
      "text": "is that they&#39;re familiar to us today."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 376340.0,
      "end_time": 378676.0,
      "text": "We see what democracy looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 378700.0,
      "end_time": 382116.0,
      "text": "We experience the effects of good government in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 382140.0,
      "end_time": 385990.0,
      "text": "just as Lorenzetti did in his life."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 386780.0,
      "end_time": 389715.0,
      "text": "But it is the allegory of bad government"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 389740.0,
      "end_time": 392100.0,
      "text": "that has been haunting me since November 9."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 393100.0,
      "end_time": 394596.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s badly damaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394620.0,
      "end_time": 396500.0,
      "text": "but it reads like today&#39;s newspapers."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 397340.0,
      "end_time": 400275.0,
      "text": "And ruling over bad government is not the Commune"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 400300.0,
      "end_time": 401500.0,
      "text": "but the Tyrant."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 402460.0,
      "end_time": 405596.0,
      "text": "He has horns, tusks, crossed eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 405620.0,
      "end_time": 407156.0,
      "text": "braided hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 407180.0,
      "end_time": 409596.0,
      "text": "He obviously spends a lot of time on that hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 409620.0,
      "end_time": 410756.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 410780.0,
      "end_time": 415750.0,
      "text": "Justice now lies helpless at his feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 415100.0,
      "end_time": 416396.0,
      "text": "shackled."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 416420.0,
      "end_time": 418220.0,
      "text": "Her scales have been severed."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 418940.0,
      "end_time": 421916.0,
      "text": "Justice is the key antagonist to the Tyrant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 421940.0,
      "end_time": 423620.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s been taken out."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 424460.0,
      "end_time": 425835.0,
      "text": "Now, surrounding the Tyrant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 425860.0,
      "end_time": 430140.0,
      "text": "Lorenzetti illustrates the vices that animate bad government."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 431100.0,
      "end_time": 434796.0,
      "text": "Avarice is the old woman clutching the strongbox"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 434820.0,
      "end_time": 436516.0,
      "text": "and a fisherman&#39;s hook"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 436540.0,
      "end_time": 438340.0,
      "text": "to pull in her fortune."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 440900.0,
      "end_time": 443916.0,
      "text": "Vainglory carries a mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 443940.0,
      "end_time": 446996.0,
      "text": "and Lorenzetti warns us against narcissistic leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 447200.0,
      "end_time": 449859.0,
      "text": "who are guided by their own ego and vanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 451340.0,
      "end_time": 453940.0,
      "text": "On the Tyrant&#39;s right is Cruelty."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 459220.0,
      "end_time": 462516.0,
      "text": "Treason, half lamb, half scorpion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 462540.0,
      "end_time": 465276.0,
      "text": "lulls us into a false sense of security"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 465300.0,
      "end_time": 467100.0,
      "text": "and then poisons a republic."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 468820.0,
      "end_time": 472200.0,
      "text": "Fraud, with the flighty wings of a bat."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 476860.0,
      "end_time": 479140.0,
      "text": "On the Tyrant&#39;s left, you see Division."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 479740.0,
      "end_time": 481660.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s dressed in Siena&#39;s colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 482600.0,
      "end_time": 485516.0,
      "text": "\"Si\" and \"No\" are painted on her body."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 485540.0,
      "end_time": 489660.0,
      "text": "She uses a carpenter&#39;s saw to chop her body in half."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 493100.0,
      "end_time": 496360.0,
      "text": "And Fury wields the weapons of the mob,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 496600.0,
      "end_time": 498180.0,
      "text": "the stone and knife."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 503100.0,
      "end_time": 505516.0,
      "text": "In the remainder of the fresco, Lorenzetti shows us"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 505540.0,
      "end_time": 507500.0,
      "text": "the inevitable effects of bad government."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 507980.0,
      "end_time": 511516.0,
      "text": "The civic ideals celebrated elsewhere in this room have failed us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 511540.0,
      "end_time": 513760.0,
      "text": "and we see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 513100.0,
      "end_time": 515836.0,
      "text": "The once beautiful city has fallen to pieces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 515860.0,
      "end_time": 517676.0,
      "text": "the countryside barren,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 517700.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519236.00000000006,
      "text": "the farms abandoned."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 519260.0,
      "end_time": 520780.0,
      "text": "Many are in flames."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 521900.0,
      "end_time": 525756.0,
      "text": "And in the sky above is not the winged figure Security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 525780.0,
      "end_time": 529435.0,
      "text": "but that of Fear, whose banner reads:"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 529460.0,
      "end_time": 532475.0,
      "text": "\"None shall pass along this road"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 532499.0,
      "end_time": 534780.0,
      "text": "without fear of death.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 537200.0,
      "end_time": 539516.0,
      "text": "Now, the final image, the most important one, really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 539540.0,
      "end_time": 541356.0,
      "text": "is one that Lorenzetti did not paint."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 541380.0,
      "end_time": 542636.0,
      "text": "It is of the viewer."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 542660.0,
      "end_time": 545435.0,
      "text": "Today, the audience for Lorenzetti&#39;s frescoes"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 545460.0,
      "end_time": 548916.0,
      "text": "is not the governing but the governed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 548940.0,
      "end_time": 551756.0,
      "text": "the individual who stands in front of his allegories"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 551780.0,
      "end_time": 554276.0,
      "text": "and walks away with insight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 554300.0,
      "end_time": 556459.0,
      "text": "who heeds a call to action."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 557340.0,
      "end_time": 560360.0,
      "text": "Lorenzetti warns us that we must recognize the shadows"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 560600.0,
      "end_time": 563955.0,
      "text": "of Avarice, Fraud, Division, even Tyranny"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 563980.0,
      "end_time": 566676.0,
      "text": "when they float across our political landscape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 566700.0,
      "end_time": 569516.0,
      "text": "especially when those shadows are cast"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 569540.0,
      "end_time": 574195.0,
      "text": "by political leaders loudly claiming to be the voice of good government"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 574220.0,
      "end_time": 577380.0,
      "text": "and promising to make America great again."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 578700.0,
      "end_time": 579900.0,
      "text": "And we must act."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 581200.0,
      "end_time": 583180.0,
      "text": "Democracy must not be a spectator sport."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 583700.0,
      "end_time": 586116.0,
      "text": "The right to protest, the right to assemble freely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 586140.0,
      "end_time": 588360.0,
      "text": "the right to petition one&#39;s government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 588600.0,
      "end_time": 589876.0,
      "text": "these are not just rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 589900.0,
      "end_time": 592396.0,
      "text": "In the face of Avarice, Fraud and Division,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 592420.0,
      "end_time": 594260.0,
      "text": "these are obligations."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 594780.0,
      "end_time": 596760.0,
      "text": "We have to disrupt --"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 596100.0,
      "end_time": 598860.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 601540.0,
      "end_time": 603716.0,
      "text": "We have to disrupt our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 603740.0,
      "end_time": 605396.0,
      "text": "so that we can disrupt"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 605420.0,
      "end_time": 608156.0,
      "text": "the amoral accretion of power"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 608180.0,
      "end_time": 612219.0,
      "text": "by those who would betray our values."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 612860.0,
      "end_time": 614756.0,
      "text": "We and we the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 614780.0,
      "end_time": 616636.0,
      "text": "must raise justice up"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 616660.0,
      "end_time": 618596.0,
      "text": "and must bring peace to our nation"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 618620.0,
      "end_time": 620796.0,
      "text": "and must come together in concord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 620820.0,
      "end_time": 622540.0,
      "text": "and we have a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 623620.0,
      "end_time": 625156.0,
      "text": "We could either paint ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 625180.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "into the worst nightmare of Lorenzetti&#39;s bad government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 629140.0,
      "end_time": 630780.0,
      "text": "or we can stay in the streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 631940.0,
      "end_time": 634900.0,
      "text": "disruptive, messy, loud."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 635500.0,
      "end_time": 637940.0,
      "text": "That is what democracy looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 638860.0,
      "end_time": 640760.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 640100.0,
      "end_time": 643300.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 651220.0,
      "end_time": 653156.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: First of all, wow."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 653180.0,
      "end_time": 655596.0,
      "text": "Obviously, many people passionately --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 655620.0,
      "end_time": 657636.0,
      "text": "you spoke to many people passionately here."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 657660.0,
      "end_time": 659396.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure there are other people here"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 659420.0,
      "end_time": 664116.0,
      "text": "who&#39;d say, look, Trump was elected by 63 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 664140.0,
      "end_time": 665476.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s far from perfect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 665500.0,
      "end_time": 668476.0,
      "text": "but he&#39;s trying to do what he was elected to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 668500.0,
      "end_time": 670600.0,
      "text": "Shouldn&#39;t you give him a chance?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 670540.0,
      "end_time": 672636.0,
      "text": "Anthony Romero: I think we have to recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 672660.0,
      "end_time": 675435.0,
      "text": "the legitimacy of him as president"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 675460.0,
      "end_time": 678356.0,
      "text": "versus the legitimacy of his policies."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 678380.0,
      "end_time": 684156.0,
      "text": "And when so many of the policies are contrary to fundamental values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 684180.0,
      "end_time": 686116.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re all equal under the law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 686140.0,
      "end_time": 689716.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re not judged by the color of our skin or the religion we worship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 689740.0,
      "end_time": 692476.0,
      "text": "we have to contest those values"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 692500.0,
      "end_time": 694756.0,
      "text": "even as we recognize and honor the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 694780.0,
      "end_time": 699260.0,
      "text": "that our democracy rendered us a president who is championing those values."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 700220.0,
      "end_time": 704360.0,
      "text": "CA: And the ACLU isn&#39;t just this force on the left, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 704600.0,
      "end_time": 706476.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re making other arguments as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 706500.0,
      "end_time": 709116.0,
      "text": "AR: Well, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 709140.0,
      "end_time": 711276.0,
      "text": "very often we piss everyone off at one point."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 711300.0,
      "end_time": 712795.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 712820.0,
      "end_time": 715236.0,
      "text": "And we recently were taking stands"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 715260.0,
      "end_time": 718596.0,
      "text": "for why Ann Coulter needs to be able to speak at Berkeley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 718620.0,
      "end_time": 721360.0,
      "text": "and why Milo has free speech rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 721600.0,
      "end_time": 722636.0,
      "text": "And we even wrote a blog"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 722660.0,
      "end_time": 726315.0,
      "text": "that almost burnt the house down among some of our members,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 726340.0,
      "end_time": 728436.0,
      "text": "unfortunately, when we talked about the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 728460.0,
      "end_time": 731916.0,
      "text": "that even Donald Trump has free speech rights as president,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 731940.0,
      "end_time": 733996.0,
      "text": "and an effort to hold him accountable"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 734200.0,
      "end_time": 738596.0,
      "text": "for incitement of violence at his marches or his rallies"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 738620.0,
      "end_time": 741796.0,
      "text": "is unconstitutional and un-American."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 741820.0,
      "end_time": 743996.0,
      "text": "And when you put that statement out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 744200.0,
      "end_time": 745675.0,
      "text": "to a very frothy base"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 745700.0,
      "end_time": 748996.0,
      "text": "that always is very excited for you to fight Donald Trump,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 749200.0,
      "end_time": 752516.0,
      "text": "and then you have a new one saying, \"Wait, these rights are for everybody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 752540.0,
      "end_time": 754435.0,
      "text": "even the president that we don&#39;t like.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 754460.0,
      "end_time": 756360.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s our job."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 756600.0,
      "end_time": 759195.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 759220.0,
      "end_time": 761796.0,
      "text": "CA: Anthony, you spoke to so many of us so powerfully."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 761820.0,
      "end_time": 763396.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 763420.0,
      "end_time": 766380.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}